posting_body: ['Medicine Lake Apartments in association with Bigos Management presents your best chance to live at the lake!!!', 'Our NEW renovations will be completed before the Fall!!', 'To access the availability and pricing for our apartments please visit our website: <URL>/', 'ONE MONTH RENT FREE!!', 'For our 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom apartment, 110.', 'Move in date by or before 08/20 for a 12 month lease or longer!', "Craig's List Special - $150 off 1st month's rent.", 'Enjoy our swimming pool, tennis court, fitness center, sauna, party room, business center, Luce Line Trail and our dock on Medicine Lake.', 'Enjoy these and the trails and parks of Medicine Lake!', 'Contact the office and set up a tour today!', '*Disclaimer:', 'Pricing and availability are determined by requested move-in date, cannot be guaranteed due to on-site leasing activity, and are subject to change at any time.']
